Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.82,0:00:12.86,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought growing older would turn me into an adult.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:12.86,0:00:13.95,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Kou-chan,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:14.61,0:00:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,how do I look?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.66,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,You laughed!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:19.66,0:00:22.29,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Suits really aren't your thing.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.29,0:00:30.71,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I'd get a job, get married, \Nand somehow become an adult version of myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.76,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}But nothing like that happened.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.06,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone! Peace signs!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.06,0:00:41.77,Default,KOCIHI,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.02,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.77,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though I've grown older,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:45.14,0:00:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.82,0:00:55.91,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've still never truly felt like I've become an adult.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.49,Default,OFFICER 1,0,0,0,,I smell a perfect crime.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:20.49,0:02:24.29,Default,OFFICER 1,0,0,0,,At the time of the crime, \Nthis room was completely locked down.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.79,Default,OFFICER 1,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are no traces of a weapon or fingerprints.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:27.79,0:02:31.75,Default,OFFICER 2,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then how did the victim die?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.46,Default,OFFICER 1,0,0,0,,{\i1}This bookcase...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.46,0:02:37.80,Default,OFFICER 1,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't they say that the victim frequented the library?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.80,0:02:38.63,Default,OFFICER 2,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.72,Default,OFFICER 1,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take a look at this book.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.72,0:02:43.30,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Hey, what are they talking about?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.39,Default,OFFICER 2,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing unusual about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:46.39,0:02:49.52,Default,OFFICER 2,0,0,0,,{\i1}We examined that one as well as this one,
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the book the victim borrowed from the library last week...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.82,Default,OFFICER 2,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.82,0:02:56.23,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.74,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.28,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,How many times have you asked that {orig: kept on talking}since we started watching?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.53,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Just shut up and watch.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.03,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I wouldn't understand anything if I didn't ask.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.03,0:03:07.29,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Telling you would just make me lose track of what's happening.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.62,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I'd lose track...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.67,0:03:12.54,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I'd lose...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.54,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.96,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.55,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Just shut up and watch, monkey!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.13,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,He's right, Chizuru-kun.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.97,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,It's about to get really interesting.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.43,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,I can't hear anything over the noise you guys are making.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.56,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,I'm going to rewind it a bit.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.56,Default,OFFICER 1,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} are the culprit, Ikegami-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.73,Default,IKEGAMI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-Where's your proof?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.07,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Sorry, I fast-forwarded.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.94,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Well, that's that.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.57,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,The mystery's been solved. Clap, clap, clap, clap, clap.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.87,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I guess this movie was a miss.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.29,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,This group's a miss!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.29,0:03:51.62,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Whose bright idea was it to watch movies at my place on Christmas Eve?!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.62,0:03:54.67,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,But we don't have the money to go out.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.59,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,And you have the biggest TV.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.05,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.93,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,We've watched all the DVDs we rented.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.93,0:04:06.10,Default,CHIZUTU,0,0,0,,We'll go rent some more, of course!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.93,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,This'll be our DVD Christmas!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.93,0:04:12.39,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Our Christmas Eve's just getting started!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.39,0:04:15.10,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Don't count on sleeping tonight!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.27,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Especially you, Kanamecchi!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.69,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,You better not talk during the movies this time.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.69,0:04:19.78,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Let me just watch in peace.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.78,0:04:23.53,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Um, let's watch the next one without any interruptions.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.03,0:04:27.03,Default,VOICE,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.04,Default,VOICE,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did it come out well?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.95,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Okay, let's switch up the order.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.87,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Kanamecchi?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.96,Default,VOICE,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next theme is: pose like a maiden in love!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.63,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,You gotta be in the photo with us.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.25,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,We already got our DVDs.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done here.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.59,0:04:42.92,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Let's go already.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.63,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.05,0:04:45.64,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.35,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:47.35,0:04:50.43,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Kanamecchi, throw up some peace signs with us!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.60,Default,VOICE,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Oh, how cute.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.81,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Like hell I will.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.81,0:04:54.06,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Why do we have to take these pictures, anyway?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.06,Default,VOICE,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Say "cheese!"
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.44,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I bet you've never done this before.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.44,Default,VOICE,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.98,0:05:00.57,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,All the cool kids are doing it.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.36,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,You're behind the times if you don't use photo booths.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.82,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who's behind the times for calling us "cool kids."
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.24,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Get ready for the next one.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.70,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,Peace signs, everyone!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.25,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun, aren't you going to do it?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Oh, how cute.{FUCK THIS BITCH, MOTHERFUCKER, RIDICULOUS GIRLlol}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.87,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What? You're terrible, Kanamecchi.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.08,0:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Say "cheese."{FUCK THIS BITCH, MOTHERFUCKER, RIDICULOUS GIRLlol}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.46,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Three, two, one...{FUCK THIS BITCH, MOTHERFUCKER, RIDICULOUS GIRLlol}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.63,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Kaname, you're so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:20.63,0:05:23.59,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,The Student Council's gonna have a physical assault case on their hands.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.42,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:24.42,0:05:28.14,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Can't we get a nice picture together?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.56,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}You can scribble on them too!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.56,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,We're supposed to choose from these?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.89,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,This one's pretty good.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.27,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,What does this button do?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Skin whitening?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.35,0:05:38.23,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Does this one make our eyes bigger?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.31,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.98,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll be outside.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.28,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.90,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.66,0:05:49.95,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Azuma-sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.16,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Huh? Azuma-sensei? Where?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.41,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Azuma-sensei!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.50,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Oh, Tachibana-kun. And the rest of you, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.13,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Buy us some pork buns!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.80,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Show us growing boys some love!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.42,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Pork buns won't make you any taller!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.17,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.55,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,A store over there.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.89,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Their croquettes looked good.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.97,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Don't just disappear like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.97,0:06:16.02,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,That's the guy from the culture festival.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.23,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,The festival...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.56,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Choco-Banana!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.40,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Choco-Banana? What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.73,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.28,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.36,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I can go wherever I want.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.36,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} guys doing here?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.53,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,We came to rent some—
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.78,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Shun-chan, you don't have to answer him.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.04,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Not only did he cut ahead of me in line at the culture festival,
Dialogue: 2,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but this jerk also insulted my height!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.71,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,You did that?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.67,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Who cares? It's all in the past.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.38,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I care!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.97,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,We don't really know what's going on here.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.97,0:06:51.39,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Azuma-sensei, how do you know him?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.30,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.30,0:06:58.98,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell you at the festival, but I guess I forgot.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.69,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,He's my friend.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.77,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I'm Akira!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.65,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Are you guys Kou-chan's students?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.23,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Your friend?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.65,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Kou-chan?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.11,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,We went to the same high school.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.32,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Homare High School.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.70,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I'm your Senpai!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.99,Default,ALL,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.45,0:07:19.46,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Azuma-sensei, you went to Homare High School?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.29,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Yes, actually.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.75,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,So this guy's the same age as you?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.00,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I thought he was around our age.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.63,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.05,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I've got a baby face,
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so people always think I'm younger than I am.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:33.18,0:07:37.01,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Your face isn't the only reason people think you're young.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.77,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Since I'm your Senpai, I expect you to show me some respect.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.06,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Especially you, little dude.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.69,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Don't call me little!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.23,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.61,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,You were taking some pictures together.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:49.61,0:07:52.61,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Oh, Sensei. Do you want one of our pictures?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.61,0:07:53.36,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.99,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Stick it on your phone so that you can always watch over your precious students.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.25,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Hey, no fair.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.96,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Give me one to put on my phone!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.17,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.42,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I bet you'd stick it on a voodoo doll!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.25,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.97,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,By the way, you're looking rather dapper today, Sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.97,0:08:11.76,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.09,0:08:15.64,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,I was at the wedding of a friend from school.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.76,0:08:20.77,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Getting married on Christmas Eve sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.85,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Right? Apparently, they met at work.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.77,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What about you, Azuma-sensei?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna marry someone you meet at work?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.02,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:29.02,0:08:31.65,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Maybe? Azuma-sensei...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell us you see your own students that way.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.78,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.49,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Akira-san, what do you do for a living?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.79,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.04,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I'm Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.42,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,A black-hearted Santa dressed in all red would make kids cry.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.38,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Well, my shift's starting soon.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.42,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.01,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Akira-san's kinda cute, isn't he?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.72,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,He's an adult, but he talks like a small child.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.68,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he actually {\i1}is{\i0} a small child.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.68,0:09:03.77,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,He said something about being Santa,\Nbut I bet he's just a jobless bum.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.77,0:09:06.06,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I bet he ran away so he wouldn't have to admit that he's broke.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.06,0:09:09.19,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Well, I should get going.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.49,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,This will probably be the last time I see you boys this year,
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so have a happy New Year.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.11,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.66,Default,ALL,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.95,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,We should go too.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.70,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I'm getting cold.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.75,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.58,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,He got us the pork buns,
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's pick up our DVD Christmas where we...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.72,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.09,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.47,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Did you fall?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.64,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Is that your balloon?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.73,Default,RISA,0,0,0,,I was holding the string, but it still flew away!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.65,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.52,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.61,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,We'll get your balloon for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:50.61,0:09:51.86,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,"We"?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.19,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Yukki, gimme a lift!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.82,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Just a little further.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.66,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,You can do it, guys!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.41,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Let's grab it and get going already.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:03.41,0:10:06.21,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Then why don't you help them?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.92,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,He said he'd get it himself.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.67,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Yukki, hold it steady!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.38,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.34,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.47,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Don't drop me.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.89,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Don't drop me, even if you lose your balance.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.05,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,"Don't drop me," you say?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.81,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Hey idiot, I'm not playing around!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.98,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Seriously, don't drop me!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.14,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,"Seriously, don't drop me," you say?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.85,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I just told you! I'm not kidding.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.52,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.57,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Um... the balloon...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.32,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Akira-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.82,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What? Choco-Banana?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.82,0:10:43.45,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Hey Chizuru, if you keep squirming like that, I really will...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.47,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Um, why are we dressed like this?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:05.47,0:11:08.64,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,It's the least you can do after ruining our event.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.64,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,You're going to repay us with hard work.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.56,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.81,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,With you guys around,
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,not only is it impossible to watch DVDs undisturbed,
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but now I can't even watch them at all.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.65,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Is this a woman's costume?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.41,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Our Christmas Eve plans!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.12,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,What did you guys think you were doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.16,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.58,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What do you think {\i1}you're{\i0} doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.58,0:11:33.29,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go cosplaying around the city, you bum!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.88,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,How rude.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.80,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I'm not playing around. This is my job.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.59,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.76,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,Akira-chan, if you had gotten here earlier it might not have happened!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.55,Default,WOMAN B,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping us out again.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.47,Default,WOMAN B,0,0,0,,We even hired a reindeer this year.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.52,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.52,0:11:55.40,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Akira-san, is it possible for you to act your age?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.11,Default,RISA,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.11,0:12:04.82,Default,RISA,0,0,0,,Mom, Santa gave me a new balloon.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.79,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Make sure you hold on tight this time.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.79,0:12:11.91,Default,RISA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.91,0:12:14.33,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Not to Yuuta's hand.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.33,0:12:17.21,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Those twins sure are popular.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.34,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}sorry{\i0} for not being as popular as them!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.63,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.47,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Looks like you guys are really popular too,
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,if you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.51,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.85,Default,CHILD A,0,0,0,,His hair's weird!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.68,Default,CHILD D,0,0,0,,I wonder if we can see her panties.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.18,Default,CHILD E,0,0,0,,Can you see them?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.14,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.19,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,You're shaking the ladder!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.15,Default,CHILD F,0,0,0,,Santa's scared.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.90,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,U-Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.90,0:12:44.03,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Can you do something about these kids for me?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.41,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.82,0:12:51.41,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Real reindeer aren't on great terms with Santa, are they?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.29,Default,CHILD F,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.25,Default,CHILD E,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.00,Default,CHILD E,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.38,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.96,Default,CHILDREN,0,0,0,,Sensei, Sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.75,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, yes. Hold on.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.75,0:13:04.72,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Ch-Choco-Banana, are you an elementary school teacher?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.89,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Of course not. I'm Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.64,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Here you go. One for each of you.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.64,0:13:10.76,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Yeah, but they just...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.18,0:13:12.93,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,It's Santa.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:12.93,0:13:16.27,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,It's the real Santa!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.48,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.69,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Santa's got a present for all you good little kids.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.53,0:13:25.15,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,What about the reindeer? Where are the reindeer?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.15,0:13:28.62,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Oh, my reindeer like to run free.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.74,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Don't talk about the reindeer like they're dogs.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.74,0:13:35.33,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,I know. I'll give you one of my caramels, Santa.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.75,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.75,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.63,Default,CHILD H,0,0,0,,Nonta, you're such a baby.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:40.63,0:13:43.17,Default,CHILD H,0,0,0,,There's no way he's the real Santa.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.09,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:44.09,0:13:47.26,Default,CHILD I,0,0,0,,He's just a normal guy dressed up like Santa.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.26,0:13:47.93,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.93,0:13:50.60,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,You're wrong! He's the real Santa!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.51,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,He's even got a white beard.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.64,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,That's right. D-Don't say such things...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.64,0:13:58.85,Default,CHILD H,0,0,0,,But that Santa Claus isn't even fat.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.85,0:14:01.65,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Even Santa is trying to get in shape these days.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.98,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Right, Santa?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.49,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Choco-Banana, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.49,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.41,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.66,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.49,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,It was just one caramel.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.16,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about the sugar!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.08,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Whatever, just put the beard back on!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.88,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,The caramel will get stuck to it.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.88,0:14:23.00,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I still haven't given you your present.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.43,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.10,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.18,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,I don't want your present!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.48,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Wait, you dropped your caramels!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.52,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,What a careless kid.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.07,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.07,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least his carelessness is a million times cuter than yours.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.41,0:14:57.04,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted. I've had enough of this.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.88,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun, you skipped out on us. {deliberate slow-down of work}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.17,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.76,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,The event's almost over, so they said I could take a break.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.26,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Huh? Really? It's over?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.39,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Chizuru, you seem to be more worn out than the rest of us.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.14,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.14,0:15:22.73,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I've been with the living eighth wonder of the world.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.77,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.19,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,Good work, boys.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.65,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,We'll take care of the rest, so you can go home.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.65,0:15:29.95,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.20,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your help.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.20,0:15:36.12,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,You can help yourselves to some \Nof the left over giveaway candy.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.12,0:15:39.12,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Really? Really?!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.50,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,First come, first serve.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.63,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Yukki, no fair.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:45.13,0:15:45.71,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:45.71,0:15:46.63,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.51,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,It's empty.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.09,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,Huh? That's odd.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.64,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,I thought there was still a lot left.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.60,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Why don't you help out again next year?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.39,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,You might get some next time.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.02,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Good work, guys.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.98,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,Akira-chan, come again next year.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.65,Default,WOMAN B,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.90,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I smell a perfect crime.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.95,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,A perfect... what?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.95,0:16:17.91,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I'm too tired to even respond to that, \Nso go be stupid somewhere else.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.95,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Just hear me out, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.66,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,The candy didn't just disappear.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.67,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,It was stolen!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.17,0:16:29.67,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,There isn't a single fingerprint at the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.67,0:16:33.43,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,There's no record of you checking for fingerprints, either.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:33.43,0:16:36.97,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Naturally, no one saw the culprit wipe off his prints.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.31,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.23,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,He must have been wearing gloves!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.98,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,We're all wearing gloves.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.19,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.32,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.69,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What I'm trying to say
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.69,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is that Choco-Banana's our prime suspect.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.20,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,In his Santa bag, that white sack,
Dialogue: 2,0:16:57.20,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,he's got the madness and greed known as the hunger for candy!{janice: these 2 lines dont rly make sense. the hunger for candy is in the bag? left unchanged for now.}
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.62,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Also, it's {\i1}our{\i0} candy in there!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.29,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.58,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.59,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Choco-Banana, show yourself!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.59,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,You're the one who's greedy here.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.97,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.97,0:17:18.01,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Sorry, he's just tired.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:18.01,0:17:20.51,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.47,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,You've seen how he acts.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.14,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,It's gotta be him!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.14,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, Chizuru-kun!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.44,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,You can't accuse him based on that!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.10,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.94,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.99,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,The reindeer?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.70,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,This smells like a perfect crime.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.79,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Hey, not you too.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.79,0:17:48.21,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,We're not the only ones who wouldn't leave fingerprints.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.75,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I told you. It was Choco-Banana.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.75,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,There's someone else.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.05,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,No. No way.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.43,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,It couldn't have been the reindeer.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.18,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,The candy...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.40,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.48,Default,REINDEER,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.90,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,J-Just take this off.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.11,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What are you doing with all of this?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.45,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,Some of our products are in there too.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.41,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,He ran away!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.70,Default,WOMAN A,0,0,0,,After him! Hurry!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.28,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Chizuru.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.37,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.34,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,Where're my caramels?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.96,Default,REINDEER,0,0,0,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.72,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.61,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.57,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,That was a bit of a surprise, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.61,0:18:59.45,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.45,0:19:02.20,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,A present from Santa for being a good little boy.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.20,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Have a merry, merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.04,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,Thanks, Santa.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.50,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,You're very welcome.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.17,Default,NONTA,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.71,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Choco-Banana...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.72,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Who {\i1}are{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.18,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I'm Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.18,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,This day has really been exhausting.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.89,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Why did I have to work so hard on Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.89,0:19:32.40,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Because you knocked over that tree.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.40,0:19:35.07,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,No, in the first place, it was...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.07,0:19:38.15,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,It was because you suggested we rent more DVDs.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.15,0:19:42.16,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,No matter how far you go back, it always comes back to Chizuru.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.62,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys wanted to watch more, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.20,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,What should we do about the DVDs?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.71,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Want to call it a night?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.37,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.37,0:19:54.21,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,This is our time now!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our DVD Christmas!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.63,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,But I don't see the DVDs in question anywhere.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.05,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Kanamecchi, where are they?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.34,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.30,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.85,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.26,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Me either.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.14,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I might have left them at the mall.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.10,Default,ALL,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:14.98,0:20:18.86,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Crap. This is so awful that I can't even muster up the strength to yell at you.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.36,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.82,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I hear jingle bells ringing in my head.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:22.82,0:20:25.16,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Yuuki-kun, that's called a headache.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.79,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Who could that be at this hour?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.41,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Maybe it's Santa.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:31.41,0:20:36.42,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Shun-chan, we graduated from believing in Santa long ago.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.25,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.34,0:20:43.51,Default,ALL,0,0,0,,Our DVDs!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.05,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Akira found them.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.47,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,You left them in the event area.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.77,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,You should be grateful.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:50.77,0:20:55.19,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Thank you, but how did you know they were ours?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:55.52,0:20:58.11,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Because they were in the picture.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:00.19,0:21:03.24,Default,ALL,0,0,0,,Santa!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.61,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I thought you just said you had graduated from that.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.20,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:09.20,0:21:13.33,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Since you came all the way here, you should enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.12,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.83,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,It looks like you were having fun.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.25,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.84,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,We've been running around all over the place,
Dialogue: 2,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're just getting started.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:21.71,0:21:23.92,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Do you drink coffee, Sensei?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.34,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.47,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I'll have a hot cocoa!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:27.47,0:21:29.22,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:29.22,0:21:33.35,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,I hope we can actually do something fun next Christmas.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.85,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll splurge a bit.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.85,0:21:40.86,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,By splurge, I bet you just mean we'll each get a single parfait.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.90,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,You underestimate me. We'll get {\i1}two{\i0} each.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.90,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,That's hardly different.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.70,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,They're so carefree.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.70,0:21:49.37,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Won't they be in the middle of their entrance exams at this time next year?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:49.37,0:21:56.08,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you can't picture that until you actually go through it.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.92,0:21:58.38,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:59.33,0:22:03.67,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought growing older would turn me into an adult.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.67,0:22:10.39,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I'd get a job, get married, \Nand somehow become an adult version of myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.43,0:22:14.39,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}But nothing like that happened.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:14.93,0:22:17.48,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,Are you jealous of them?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:17.48,0:22:19.02,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.82,Default,AKIRA,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to be high schoolers again.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:21.82,0:22:23.40,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:25.40,0:22:30.91,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've still never truly felt that I've become an adult.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.91,0:22:34.70,Default,KOICHI,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I know I'm no longer a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.97,0:24:20.18,Default,TEXT,0,0,0,,Next time: "In The Steam."
